videos.description: Nico Clareth pulls up and hits the 3 from the top of the key to give Siena a 10-6 lead.
videos.headline: Siena's Clareth drains the deep 3

videos.description: Ahsante Shivers takes it to the hole with the power move and finishes with acrobatic shot.
videos.headline: Shivers drives strong to the hoop for 2

videos.description: Nico Clareth's turnover leads to a transition lay-in for Iona's Sam Cassell Jr.
videos.headline: Clareth's turnover leads to transition layup for Iona

videos.description: Ahsante Shivers rebounds Marquis Wright's missed 3 pointer and finishes for 2.
videos.headline: Shivers skies for follow up basket

videos.description: Siena guard Lavon Long comes down with the offensive board, and then gets the putback shot to fall, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Long grabs the offensive rebound and gets the puback for Siena

videos.description: Schadrac Casimir hits the 3 to give Iona a 45-42 lead.
videos.headline: Iona's Casimir drains 3 from the wing

videos.description: Deyshonee Much hits the fall jumper to give Iona a 54-48 lead.
videos.headline: Much too Much

videos.description: Marquis Wright hits a big 3-pointer to put Siena up 59-57, part of an 11-0 Saints run.
videos.headline: Wright puts Siena up two points with under 10 minutes to go.

videos.description: Deyshonee  Much makes the steal and goes the length of the court for the jam.
videos.headline: Much gets the steal and dunk

videos.description: Siena's Marquis Wright drains a clutch 3-pointer after a crazy sequence of events.
videos.headline: Wright sinks 3-pointer late to tie game

videos.description: Jordan Washington flips ball up and in to give Iona a two point overtime lead.
videos.headline: Washington makes off balance shot

videos.description: Deyshonee Much drives and gets the floater to fall late in OT.
videos.headline: Much puts Iona up by 2 late in OT

videos.description: EJ Crawford drives through a crowd and makes layup to give Iona 85-83 lead in overtime.
videos.headline: Crawford's driving layup gives Iona late lead

videos.description: Nico Clareth misses the late 3-pointer to tie in OT as Siena falls to Iona, 87-86.
videos.headline: Siena's Clareth misses 3-point attempt with the game on the line
